00:18:24,130 --> 00:18:27,780
One day, you will understand.

268
00:18:27,780 --> 00:18:31,160
When life forces you to choose

269
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:36,380
between your duty and your heart.

270
00:18:44,750 --> 00:18:46,550
I...

271
00:18:49,660 --> 00:18:51,760
I'm sorry...

272
00:18:53,190 --> 00:18:57,020
that I love myself more than you.

273
00:19:32,760 --> 00:19:34,070
It's all done.

274
00:19:34,070 --> 00:19:35,180
Thank you.

275
00:19:35,180 --> 00:19:37,200
I'll help you carry the bag.

276
00:19:44,240 --> 00:19:45,610
Khun Nueng.

277
00:19:45,610 --> 00:19:47,770
How is the account balance?

278
00:19:47,770 --> 00:19:50,240
Do we have money to pay the debt?

279
00:19:50,240 --> 00:19:53,340
No.

280
00:19:53,340 --> 00:19:57,650
If we have more guests, we may have money to pay it off.

281
00:19:59,090 --> 00:20:00,670
It's okay.

282
00:20:00,670 --> 00:20:04,990
The weather is getting better. There will be more visitors coming here.

283
00:20:05,820 --> 00:20:10,373
Here is your accommodation. I'll go and check in for you.

284
00:20:12,840 --> 00:20:15,303
Palm. Nuengdiao.

285
00:20:15,940 --> 00:20:17,640
Maggie.

286
00:20:23,440 --> 00:20:24,500
What are you doing here?

287
00:20:24,500 --> 00:20:27,570
I told you that I work as an assistant guide.

288
00:20:27,570 --> 00:20:30,160
I brought my guests here for a beach vacation.

289
00:20:30,160 --> 00:20:32,370
They booked rooms here. So I gave them a ride.

290
00:20:32,370 --> 00:20:34,180
But I'm staying at another place.

291
00:20:34,180 --> 00:20:36,890
Palm, what are you doing here?

292
00:20:38,040 --> 00:20:40,320
This is my mom's hostel.

293
00:20:40,320 --> 00:20:41,580
Really?

294
00:20:41,580 --> 00:20:43,880
It's a very cute hostel.

295
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:46,810
That's too bad. I already booked a room at another place.

296
00:20:46,810 --> 00:20:49,630
If I had known, I would have booked a room here.

297
00:20:51,260 --> 00:20:52,280
It's okay.

298
00:20:52,280 --> 00:20:54,990
My work for today is done. Now, I have free time.

299
00:20:54,990 --> 00:20:56,500
Are you guys free?

300
00:20:56,500 --> 00:20:58,200
Palm, are you free?

301
00:20:59,057 --> 00:21:00,530
After checking in your guests, I'll be free.

302
00:21:00,530 --> 00:21:03,300
Okay. I'll wait.

303
00:21:03,300 --> 00:21:05,620
Can you take me around the island?

304
00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:09,800
Okay.

305
00:21:13,040 --> 00:21:15,959
- Did you book the rooms under your name?
- Yes.

306
00:21:15,959 --> 00:21:17,910
It's for two rooms, right?

307
00:21:22,210 --> 00:21:25,120
Palm, take the guests to their rooms.

308
00:21:27,760 --> 00:21:29,760
Please follow me.

309
00:21:37,200 --> 00:21:38,700
Nuengdiao.

310
00:21:38,700 --> 00:21:40,900
How are you? Are you doing all right?

311
00:21:40,900 --> 00:21:44,763
It's okay. I'm fine. So chill.

312
00:21:44,763 --> 00:21:48,063
Are you working as a receptionist at the hostel?

313
00:21:48,063 --> 00:21:49,080
Yes.

314
00:21:49,080 --> 00:21:53,180
Palm's mom gave us a room to stay in, so we help her around to pay her back.

315
00:21:53,180 --> 00:21:57,000
You are not someone who needs to do all this hard work.

316
00:21:57,000 --> 00:21:59,500
Unless you are on the run.

317
00:22:02,400 --> 00:22:04,370
Maggie.

318
00:22:04,370 --> 00:22:06,290
Shall we go now?

319
00:22:06,290 --> 00:22:07,800
Khun Nueng, do you want to come with us?

320
00:22:07,800 --> 00:22:10,903
It's okay. I'll stay and take care of the guests.

321
00:22:12,410 --> 00:22:15,810
Then see you later, Nuengdiao.

322
00:22:15,810 --> 00:22:17,980
sure.

323
00:22:18,010 --> 00:22:19,810
Let's go.

324
00:22:25,620 --> 00:22:28,100
I saw the news.

325
00:22:28,100 --> 00:22:30,400
Police are looking for you and Nuengdiao.

326
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:32,800
I've never thought that you would run this far.

327
00:22:32,800 --> 00:22:34,940
You came all the way to this island.

328
00:22:36,380 --> 00:22:39,790
How long do you need to be his bodyguard?

329
00:22:40,960 --> 00:22:46,020
Until Khun Nueng is safe and the problem back in Bangkok is solved.

330
00:22:47,050 --> 00:22:49,470
How long will that take?

331
00:22:50,820 --> 00:22:52,420
Maggie.

332
00:22:53,040 --> 00:22:58,020
Can you promise that you won't tell anyone that Khun Nueng and I are staying here?

333
00:23:01,990 --> 00:23:03,550
I'm serious.

334
00:23:03,550 --> 00:23:06,010
Khun Nueng can be in danger.

335
00:23:07,110 --> 00:23:09,370
You're only worried about him.

336
00:23:09,370 --> 00:23:13,180
All you think about is Nuengdiao.

337
00:23:13,180 --> 00:23:16,367
This is not a favor that you can ask for free.

338
00:23:16,367 --> 00:23:19,540
You need to bribe me.

339
00:23:24,440 --> 00:23:26,140
Where is the money?

340
00:23:26,760 --> 00:23:29,220
Let's take more photos.

341
00:23:43,210 --> 00:23:45,800
1, 2, 3.

342
00:24:00,420 --> 00:24:02,960
What are you doing here?

343
00:24:02,960 --> 00:24:05,960
I'm just taking pictures. I thought the place looks nice.

344
00:24:05,960 --> 00:24:07,580
You can't take pictures here.

345
00:24:07,580 --> 00:24:08,740
Delete the pictures right now.

346
00:24:08,740 --> 00:24:11,740
This is a film camera, not a digital one. The pictures can't be deleted.

347
00:24:11,740 --> 00:24:14,290
- Then give me the film.
- But this is my camera.

348
00:24:14,290 --> 00:24:16,080
- Give it to me.
- Let my camera go.

349
00:24:16,080 --> 00:24:17,171
Let it go.

350
00:24:17,171 --> 00:24:18,810
Palm, help me.

351
00:24:18,810 --> 00:24:20,881
What are you doing? Let her go.

352
00:24:20,881 --> 00:24:22,600
Stay out of it.

353
00:24:22,600 --> 00:24:24,500
Don't butt in.

354
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:31,960
Are you all right, Maggie?

355
00:24:31,960 --> 00:24:33,870
Get up slowly.

356
00:24:34,860 --> 00:24:37,090
Are you all right? Get up slowly.

357
00:24:37,090 --> 00:24:38,930
Palm.

358
00:24:39,940 --> 00:24:43,443
- Palm, run!
- Let's run.

359
00:24:45,450 --> 00:24:46,710
Hey!

360
00:24:46,710 --> 00:24:48,630
What is going on?

361
00:24:48,630 --> 00:24:50,560
The noise is so loud and gets into the gambling house.

362
00:24:50,560 --> 00:24:54,130
Teenagers took pictures here.

363
00:24:54,130 --> 00:24:56,040
Who are they?

364
00:24:56,040 --> 00:24:57,810
We know everyone on the island.

365
00:24:57,810 --> 00:24:59,610
I don't know them.

366
00:24:59,610 --> 00:25:01,880
I think they are tourists.

367
00:25:01,880 --> 00:25:04,760
But the kid who kicked you looks familiar.

368
00:25:04,760 --> 00:25:07,690
I saw him at the hostel owned by Mam, our debtor.

369
00:25:07,690 --> 00:25:10,680
That's why he looks familiar.

370
00:25:10,680 --> 00:25:13,017
He must be Mam's son.

371
00:25:14,648 --> 00:25:16,520
Mam's son?

372
00:25:16,520 --> 00:25:20,430
She is my debtor and hasn't paid the money back, right?

373
00:25:21,670 --> 00:25:24,360
I'll teach you a lesson.

374
00:25:24,360 --> 00:25:27,100
How dare you cause trouble on my turf?

375
00:25:31,220 --> 00:25:34,120
You shouldn't have fought with them.

376
00:25:34,880 --> 00:25:37,020
They would never listen to us.

377
00:25:37,020 --> 00:25:39,120
They would use force on us anyway.

378
00:25:39,120 --> 00:25:43,880
It's just a camera. Your life is more important.

379
00:25:43,880 --> 00:25:46,050
Let me take a look.

380
00:25:46,050 --> 00:25:48,110
Does it hurt?

381
00:25:52,830 --> 00:25:54,520
Nuengdiao.

382
00:25:54,520 --> 00:25:56,250
Are you all right?

383
00:25:56,250 --> 00:25:58,510
Thank you for helping me.

384
00:25:58,510 --> 00:26:02,303
It's okay. I'm glad that you got your camera back.

385
00:26:02,303 --> 00:26:04,660
How did you come to help us in time?

386
00:26:04,660 --> 00:26:06,390
When did you get there?

387
00:26:06,390 --> 00:26:08,360
I told you that I would come see you later.

388
00:26:08,360 --> 00:26:11,030
When I got there, I saw you were in trouble.

389
00:26:11,030 --> 00:26:12,540
So I stepped in to help you.

390
00:26:12,540 --> 00:26:13,440
I got used to it.

391
00:26:13,440 --> 00:26:16,940
After spending a lot of time with Palm, I realized I need to learn these things.

392
00:26:18,120 --> 00:26:21,281
It's good that he had a chance to protect someone else other than me.

393
00:26:24,770 --> 00:26:26,770
I have to go now.

394
00:26:27,690 --> 00:26:30,644
Khun Nueng, do you want me to give you a ride?

395
00:26:33,672 --> 00:26:36,672
It's okay. You should stay with Maggie.

396
00:26:57,616 --> 00:27:00,492
Can I ask you something?

397
00:27:00,492 --> 00:27:04,908
Don't you feel frustrated that you need to hide your feelings?

398
00:27:05,660 --> 00:27:07,560
What feelings?

399
00:27:08,960 --> 00:27:11,800
The feelings that you have for Nuengdiao.

400
00:27:11,800 --> 00:27:13,630
Don't you feel frustrated?

401
00:27:15,632 --> 00:27:17,110
Why do you look so surprised?

402
00:27:17,110 --> 00:27:21,628
The way you look at him and treat him says it all.

403
00:27:21,628 --> 00:27:23,770
It says you love Nuengdiao.

404
00:27:24,896 --> 00:27:26,515
How do you know that I love Nuengdiao?

405
00:27:26,515 --> 00:27:29,183
I've never said that.

406
00:27:29,183 --> 00:27:31,916
It's so obvious.

407
00:27:31,916 --> 00:27:35,676
You can lie to yourself, but you cannot lie to me.

408
00:27:35,676 --> 00:27:39,504
I can tell how you feel. I noticed since we were at the dance club.

409
00:27:41,360 --> 00:27:45,480
Every time you looked at Nuengdiao when he played the piano,

410
00:27:45,480 --> 00:27:47,929
it was the way a man looked at his lover.

411
00:27:54,130 --> 00:28:00,163
When you were dancing with me, your eyes kept looking at Nuengdiao.

412
00:28:06,020 --> 00:28:09,268
It was like your whole world was him.

413
00:28:10,576 --> 00:28:15,156
I understand it. You are crazy in love.

414
00:28:15,156 --> 00:28:17,484
I've been through it before.

415
00:28:17,484 --> 00:28:19,744
I had a crush on you at first.

416
00:28:19,744 --> 00:28:22,648
But after I saw the way you looked at him on the first day you came to the dance club,

417
00:28:22,648 --> 00:28:25,176
I knew I didn't have a chance.

418
00:28:25,176 --> 00:28:27,741
It's better to befriend you.

419
00:28:28,550 --> 00:28:30,940
Because I have a bright personality.

420
00:28:30,940 --> 00:28:34,788
So people misunderstood thinking I was flirting with you.

421
00:28:36,840 --> 00:28:38,860
Thank you, Maggie.

422
00:28:40,440 --> 00:28:42,296
No problem.

423
00:28:46,830 --> 00:28:50,080
[Phoomphiphat Wittayalai High Schoo]l

424
00:29:01,704 --> 00:29:04,632
Hey! What are you doing here?

425
00:29:05,627 --> 00:29:06,864
Do you have a swimming class?

426
00:29:06,864 --> 00:29:09,580
No. I'm here to see you.

427
00:29:09,580 --> 00:29:13,170
Why? Did you start get into fights?

428
00:29:13,170 --> 00:29:15,304
Are you here to take me to get into another fight?

429
00:29:15,304 --> 00:29:16,684
Are you crazy?

430
00:29:16,684 --> 00:29:18,124
I'm a peaceful man.

431
00:29:18,124 --> 00:29:22,412
If they don't look for trouble with me, I won't start a fight with them.

432
00:29:23,440 --> 00:29:27,172
What do you want from watching me swimming?

433
00:29:29,616 --> 00:29:32,080
I...

434
00:29:32,080 --> 00:29:34,148
I have something I want to talk to you about.

435
00:29:34,148 --> 00:29:35,748
Is it something serious?

436
00:29:36,560 --> 00:29:40,972
Serious? Yes, it's very serious.

437
00:29:43,300 --> 00:29:47,228
It's about us.

438
00:30:00,724 --> 00:30:02,740
What are you looking at?

439
00:30:02,740 --> 00:30:04,752
To be honest,

440
00:30:04,752 --> 00:30:08,840
when we were in 10th grade, I never thought that you were good-looking.

441
00:30:08,840 --> 00:30:11,720
I've never been your type.

442
00:30:15,660 --> 00:30:17,200
Should we go talk outside?

443
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:18,472
I'm done.

444
00:30:18,472 --> 00:30:19,990
Sure.

445
00:30:19,990 --> 00:30:21,390
Let's go.

446
00:30:24,280 --> 00:30:27,080
What is the serious thing you want to talk to me about?

447
00:30:27,976 --> 00:30:31,620
I want to thank you.

448
00:30:31,620 --> 00:30:34,330
For helping me find the person who exposed Nuengdiao and me.

449
00:30:34,330 --> 00:30:37,688
This is the serious thing that you want to talk about?

450
00:30:37,688 --> 00:30:40,864
Nueng is my cousin. You are my friend.

451
00:30:40,864 --> 00:30:43,020
I had every reason to help you.

452
00:30:44,488 --> 00:30:48,280
Do you have any updates on Nuengdiao?

453
00:30:48,280 --> 00:30:50,532
Is your dad looking for him?

454
00:30:55,430 --> 00:30:56,730
Yes..

455
00:30:57,400 --> 00:31:00,500
My dad sent his men to look for him.

456
00:31:02,600 --> 00:31:04,589
He will be back soon.

457
00:31:04,589 --> 00:31:06,996
He will come back and date you again.

458
00:31:11,472 --> 00:31:13,024
I...

459
00:31:13,024 --> 00:31:15,584
I have another thing I want to ask you.

460
00:31:16,848 --> 00:31:18,548
What is it?

461
00:31:21,304 --> 00:31:26,044
Do you still like me?

462
00:31:28,156 --> 00:31:30,056
Why do you ask me that?

463
00:31:31,104 --> 00:31:33,244
I'm just curious.

464
00:31:33,244 --> 00:31:37,028
I want to apologize to you.

465
00:31:37,028 --> 00:31:40,288
That I rejected you when you confessed your feelings to me.

466
00:31:41,020 --> 00:31:44,296
After that, you kept a distance from me.

467
00:31:44,930 --> 00:31:47,630
What did you want me to do?

468
00:31:47,630 --> 00:31:53,270
Staying close to the guy that I liked, but he didn't feel the same way.

469
00:31:53,270 --> 00:31:55,270
It was awkward.

470
00:31:56,876 --> 00:31:58,976
I get it.

471
00:32:00,224 --> 00:32:05,780
You are helping me and Nuengdiao.

472
00:32:05,780 --> 00:32:07,632
Don't you feel hurt?

473
00:32:07,632 --> 00:32:12,132
Or don't you have feelings for me anymore?

474
00:32:16,910 --> 00:32:19,240
Why do you want to know that?

475
00:32:19,240 --> 00:32:21,290
Just know that I'm okay now.

476
00:32:21,290 --> 00:32:24,084
Forget about what happened in the past.

477
00:32:27,592 --> 00:32:32,016
If I told you I rejected you back then,

478
00:32:32,016 --> 00:32:35,250
because I couldn't admit to myself who I am.

479
00:32:35,250 --> 00:32:40,564
But now I know how I really feel.

480
00:32:43,890 --> 00:32:46,400
♫ I couldn't stopp ♫

481
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:48,980
Do you still have feelings for me?

482
00:32:49,880 --> 00:32:53,140
♫ But that has changed now ♫

483
00:33:02,800 --> 00:33:03,880
Move. Come with us.

484
00:33:03,880 --> 00:33:05,610
I'm not going.

485
00:33:05,610 --> 00:33:07,510
Where are you taking her?

486
00:33:08,420 --> 00:33:10,350
- It's none of your business.
- Khun Nueng.

487
00:33:10,350 --> 00:33:13,068
Palm. Your mom.

488
00:33:14,192 --> 00:33:16,831
Mom. Hey!
- Palm!
- Mom!

489
00:33:16,831 --> 00:33:18,663
- Palm. Palm!
- Mom.

490
00:33:18,663 --> 00:33:20,168
Hey!

491
00:33:23,880 --> 00:33:24,928
Hey.

492
00:33:24,928 --> 00:33:26,510
Where are you going?

493
00:33:26,510 --> 00:33:28,753
I'm here looking for my mom. Where did you take her?

494
00:33:28,753 --> 00:33:31,536
My boss put your mom to work so she can pay back her debt.

495
00:33:31,536 --> 00:33:33,996
How the hell can you do that to my mom?

496
00:33:35,030 --> 00:33:36,630
Palm.

497
00:33:38,748 --> 00:33:40,768
Do you think you are some hotshot? Huh?

498
00:33:40,768 --> 00:33:42,946
Do you want to die?

499
00:33:44,416 --> 00:33:47,250
Calm down.

500
00:33:47,250 --> 00:33:49,016
Don't shoot him in the gambling house.

501
00:33:49,016 --> 00:33:53,096
If there's a body here, I will need to smooth things out with the police.

502
00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:56,790
He's here to look for his mom, Boss.

503
00:33:58,720 --> 00:34:01,000
Hey, come here.

504
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:02,360
Let me go.

505
00:34:02,360 --> 00:34:05,240
- Mom.
- Palm, don't.

506
00:34:06,150 --> 00:34:08,296
Your son is quite daring.

507
00:34:08,296 --> 00:34:10,144
He's such a devoted son.

508
00:34:10,144 --> 00:34:11,700
He came here to rescue you.

509
00:34:11,700 --> 00:34:14,302
Palm, you don't have to rescue me.

510
00:34:14,302 --> 00:34:17,657
Go home. I can take care of it.

511
00:34:17,657 --> 00:34:20,440
Stay away from these men.

512
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:22,924
I'll find the money to pay them back.

513
00:34:22,924 --> 00:34:25,460
How will you find the money?

514
00:34:25,460 --> 00:34:30,430
I gave you a lot of time to pay it back, but you can't do it.

515
00:34:30,430 --> 00:34:33,775
I want my money back today.

516
00:34:38,864 --> 00:34:44,391
If you can't pay me back, you need to work for me to pay your debt.

517
00:34:46,760 --> 00:34:52,056
In my opinion, though you are a bit old,

518
00:34:52,056 --> 00:34:54,857
you still look pretty.

519
00:34:55,570 --> 00:34:57,690
Your body is still in shape.

520
00:34:57,690 --> 00:34:59,680
Asshole, you cannot do that to my mom!

521
00:34:59,680 --> 00:35:01,220
Why?

522
00:35:01,220 --> 00:35:03,184
Why can't I do that?

523
00:35:03,184 --> 00:35:05,395
I opened an illegal gambling house,

524
00:35:05,395 --> 00:35:07,815
But the police cannot do anything about it.

525
00:35:07,815 --> 00:35:11,266
Do you think I am afraid of anyone? Huh?

526
00:35:13,048 --> 00:35:16,902
Your son is brave, but he is a bit dull-witted.

527
00:35:19,860 --> 00:35:23,310
- Palm
- If you don't want your mom to become a prostitute,

528
00:35:23,310 --> 00:35:25,960
you need to pay me back.

529
00:35:25,960 --> 00:35:28,622
If you can't find the money by the end of the day,

530
00:35:28,622 --> 00:35:31,642
brace yourself for a new father.

531
00:35:33,168 --> 00:35:35,490
- Palm.
- Let's go.

532
00:35:36,260 --> 00:35:37,751
Palm.

533
00:35:37,751 --> 00:35:39,751
