534
00:35:41,493 --> 00:35:43,628
What are you going to do?

535
00:35:43,628 --> 00:35:46,328
Where are you going to get the money?

536
00:35:46,328 --> 00:35:48,280
Why don't we call Uncle Non?

537
00:35:48,280 --> 00:35:50,400
I tried to call my dad,

538
00:35:50,400 --> 00:35:54,320
but I couldn't reach him. I don't know if something happened to him.

539
00:35:54,320 --> 00:35:57,132
I have money in my account. But I need to get it from an ATM.

540
00:35:57,132 --> 00:35:59,591
It's too risky to do that.

541
00:35:59,591 --> 00:36:01,795
What will you do if Khun Suphakit finds out?

542
00:36:01,795 --> 00:36:03,706
It's not time to worry about me.

543
00:36:03,706 --> 00:36:05,640
You should be worried about your family.

544
00:36:05,640 --> 00:36:08,830
