589
00:40:07,850 --> 00:40:12,690
But I promise that I will pay you back as soon as possible.

590
00:40:12,690 --> 00:40:16,155
It's okay. You don't need to pay it back.

591
00:40:16,155 --> 00:40:17,200
No, I can't do that.

592
00:40:17,200 --> 00:40:19,351
I don't like to owe anyone anything.

593
00:40:19,351 --> 00:40:22,560
You paid the debt for me, I need to pay you back.

594
00:40:22,560 --> 00:40:25,520
Don't try to be a saint rescuing others.

595
00:40:25,520 --> 00:40:27,777
I don't like it.

596
00:40:27,777 --> 00:40:31,097
Mama Mam, you can pay it back whenever you have the money.

597
00:40:33,984 --> 00:40:39,086
Now I get why you want to protect him so much.

598
00:40:41,180 --> 00:40:44,202
He's nice and cute.

599
00:40:45,750 --> 00:40:49,777
