605
00:41:06,840 --> 00:41:10,704
Please let me call you that. It sounds cute.

606
00:41:10,704 --> 00:41:14,117
I also miss my mom.

607
00:41:14,117 --> 00:41:17,538
If you are not okay with it, I can go back and call you aunt.

608
00:41:17,538 --> 00:41:19,000
You can call me whatever you want.

609
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:21,110
